disabling button using id, can be done with TagName[postion] 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>button</title>
</head>
<body>
	<p>button gets disabled onclick</p>
	<button id = 'main' onclick="myfunction()">clicker</button>
<script type="text/javascript">
	function myfunction(){
		document.getElementById('main').disabled = true;
	}
</script>
</body>
</html>
